title: Athletics at the 2013 Southeast Asian Games – Men's discus throw
text: The men's discus throw at the <a href="2013%20Southeast%20Asian%20Games">2013 Southeast Asian Games</a>, the <a href="Athletics%20%28sport%29">athletics</a> was held in <a href="Naypyidaw">Naypyidaw</a>, <a href="Burma">Myanmar</a>. The <a href="track%20and%20field">track and field</a> events is taking place at the <a href="Wunna%20Theikdi%20Stadium">Wunna Theikdi Stadium</a>on December 15.
